id: "class:fighter#shielded_fighter"
name: "Shielded Fighter"
description: "A shielded fighter focuses on both offense and defense, blending weapon\
  \ and shield in perfect balance to impede his enemies while delivering deadly blows,\
  \ and even turning the shield itself into a formidable weapon. These fighting school\
  \ benefits apply when wielding a weapon and a shield simultaneously."
modifications:
- add: "ability:active_defense#fighter_shielded_fighter"
  remove:
  - "ability:armor_training#fighter"
